# MotionFolio environment variables (EXAMPLE)
#
# Copy this file to ".env" and fill in your values:
#   cp .env.example .env
#
# The AI terminal assistant is OPTIONAL. Local terminal commands (help, ls,
# cat <slug>, ...) work WITHOUT any key. The AI chat only activates when a key
# is present below.
#
# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# ⚠️  SECURITY WARNING — read before deploying ⚠️
# Vite inlines every VITE_* / REACT_APP_* variable into the CLIENT BUNDLE, so any
# key set here is shipped to the browser and is PUBLICLY READABLE on a deployed
# site. This is DEMO-ONLY. For production, do NOT expose a private key here — use a
# server-side / serverless proxy that holds the key as a server secret.
# See docs/ai-terminal.md and SECURITY.md.
# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

# Primary key (Groq — free at https://console.groq.com):
VITE_GROQ_API_KEY=
